<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Reset Your Password</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f9f9fb;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #4c1d95;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .header img {
        max-height: 50px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 32px;
      }
      .content h1 {
        font-size: 22px;
        color: #4c1d95;
        margin-bottom: 18px;
      }
      .content p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #7c3aed;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 14px 24px;
        margin: 30px 0;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 15px;
      }
      .footer {
        background-color: #f3f4f6;
        padding: 24px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #6b7280;
      }
      .footer a {
        color: #7c3aed;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <img src="cid:semicek-logo" alt="Semicek Innovations" />
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h1>Reset Your Password</h1>
        <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
        <p>
          You recently requested to reset your password for your Semicek Innovations account.
          Click the button below to proceed. This link is valid for 1 hour.
        </p>
        <p style="text-align: center;">
          <a href="{{resetLink}}" class="button">Reset Password</a>
        </p>
        <p>
          If you didn’t request this, you can safely ignore this email — no changes will be made.
        </p>
        <p>Best,<br />The Semicek Innovations Team</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        &copy; {{year}} Semicek Innovations. All rights reserved.<br />
        <a href="mailto:support@semicekinnovations.com">Need help?</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
